<li><a href="http://www.hrc.utexas.edu/multimedia/video/2008/wallace/niebuhr_reinhold.html" class="external text" title="http://www.hrc.utexas.edu/multimedia/video/2008/wallace/niebuhr_reinhold.html" rel="nofollow">Reinhold Niebuhr: April 27, 1958 Interview</a>, <a href="/wiki/The_Mike_Wallace_Interview" title="The Mike Wallace Interview">The Mike Wallace Interview</a> collection, <a href="/wiki/The_University_of_Texas_at_Austin" title="The University of Texas at Austin" class="mw-redirect">The University of Texas at Austin</a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.time.com/time/covers/0,16641,19480308,00.html" class="external text" title="http://www.time.com/time/covers/0,16641,19480308,00.html" rel="nofollow">"Reinhold Niebuhr"</a>, <i>Time</i> Magazine Cover (Mar. 8 1948)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.nybooks.com/articles/22472" class="external text" title="http://www.nybooks.com/articles/22472" rel="nofollow">Brian Urquhart, "What You Can Learn from Reinhold Niebuhr"</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/The_New_York_Review_of_Books" title="The New York Review of Books">The New York Review of Books</a></i></li>
</ul>


